	 <title>System.SubString</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This operator returns a string that is a part, or substring of, the
		  given string.</para> 
	 <note> 
		  <para>D4 uses zero based strings.</para> 
	 </note> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select TableDee add { "Data" + SubString("Alphora", 2, 4) Copied };</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>Copied
--------
Dataphor</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
	 <formalpara> 
		  <title>See Also</title> 
		  <para><ulink url="D4LGUsingStrings.html">Using Strings</ulink></para> 
	 </formalpara> 
</sect2> 
